{"tid":2508690,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「人生課程」=「精神傳銷」毀你一生","createTime":"2021-04-29T03:04:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T03:59:37.000Z","uid":265168,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3ad74d2bcbf575f2e619b782bf794e6f3627d76a","tid":2508690,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T03:04:26.000Z","msg":"當你身邊朋友、同事、家人變得異常正面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「上堂」後變得疲倦不堪、聲線沙啞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「上堂」上到凌晨，身邊開始出現一班「學員」<br />\n所謂「導師」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n並開始拉身邊既人一齊「上堂」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你就要俾佢睇下以下文章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「我突然從此前的渾沌中醒悟過來：<span class=\"red\">課程的本質實際上是以一些強有力的心理手段來控制我們，然後利用我們的激情去為公司&ldquo;拉客&rdquo;。</span><br />\n<br />\n第一階段，課程要我們&ldquo;放下 分析、評估和判斷&rdquo;即放棄理性，讓我們成為&ldquo;空杯子&rdquo;；<br />\n第二階段，課程摧毀我們原有的心理結構，給我們的&ldquo;空杯&rdquo;中注滿新的&ldquo;水&rdquo;，其本質上是讓我們形成 &ldquo;課程是挽救我們生命的惟一途徑&rdquo;、&rdquo;課程至上&rdquo;的觀念；<br />\n第三階段，則是利用我們去發展新學員。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />台灣Blogger深入剖析 「人生課程」<br />\n<a href=\"https://gn00116743.pixnet.net/blog/post/39928585-%E7%9F%A5%E8%AD%98--%22%E6%B4%97%E8%85%A6%E8%AA%B2%E7%A8%8B%22-%E4%B8%89%E9%9A%8E%E6%AE%B5%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%21-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgn00116743.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F39928585-%25E7%259F%25A5%25E8%25AD%2598--%2522%25E6%25B4%2597%25E8%2585%25A6%25E8%25AA%25B2%25E7%25A8%258B%2522-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%259A%258E%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E5%25AE%258C%25E6%2595%25B4%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%259E%2590%2521-&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzSLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=0c9784a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://gn00116743.pixnet.net/blog/post/39928585-%E7%9F%A5%E8%AD%98--%22%E6%B4%97%E8%85%A6%E8%AA%B2%E7%A8%8B%22-%E4%B8%89%E9%9A%8E%E6%A